org.apache.taverna.workflowmodel.processor.iteration.impl

Class IterationStrategyStackImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.taverna.workflowmodel.processor.iteration.impl.IterationStrategyStackImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IterationStrategyStack, WorkflowItem

    public class IterationStrategyStackImpl
extends Object
implements IterationStrategyStack
    Contains an ordered list of IterationStrategyImpl objects. The top of the list is fed data directly, all other nodes are fed complete Job objects and Completion events from the layer above. The bottom layer pushes events onto the processor event queue to be consumed by the dispatch stack.
    Author:
    Tom Oinn
